Now in business: the #EQE is the first all-electric business saloon with luxury-class electric architecture from Mercedes-EQ.

Find out more about our newest #MercedesEQ family member.

#MercedesBenz #MercedesEQ #progressiveluxury #MBIAA21 #IAA21

Angaben zum Stromverbrauch und zur Reichweite sind vorläufig und wurden intern nach Maßgabe der Zertifizierungsmethode „WLTP-Prüfverfahren“ ermittelt. Es liegen bislang weder bestätigte Werte vom TÜV noch eine EG-Typgenehmigung noch eine Konformitätsbescheinigung mit amtlichen Werten vor. Abweichungen zwischen den Angaben und den amtlichen Werten sind möglich.

Every time sport defeats disadvantage, everyone wins.

For 20 years, we’ve believed that sport powerfully unites us and can uniquely engage young people and children; through sport, millions have been able to access the change programmes they’ve desperately needed to help move their lives forwards.

Together with Laureus Sport For Good, the programmes we support tackle the most challenging social problems frustrating the futures of young people and children in our local communities: health and mental wellbeing; access to education; women and girl’s equality; employability; inclusivity for the marginalized; and ending violence.

#Laureus #SportforGood #Everyonewins #Changethegameforkids #MercedesBenz

At first glance, @jesshart's modelling career reads like a fairy-tale success story. But it took the Australian-born model years to realize her true passion. To us, she is unapologetic about admitting that her heart beats more for smoking wheels than for the smoke and mirrors of the fashion world. In our new episode of AMG Uncovered, Jess explains how important it was to overcome the common stereotypes in order to unlock her true self.

Music: 86Tales

The endurance test drive department is quite an institution in the vehicle development at Mercedes-Benz. Which high demands does a luxury EV of Mercedes-EQ need to comply with before being released to the market? Andreas Frank is a test driver at Mercedes-Benz and he tests the #EQS under extreme conditions.

The web series "Unexpected Beauty" offers an exclusive excursion behind the scenes of the challenging and passionate development of the EQS by @mercedeseq.

All participants have been tested for COVID-19 with negative results.

node.text:
Safety in the new S-Class is really next-level. Partly because the Driving Assistance System comes as standard. That basically means: modern sensors with greater range enable higher safety.

Enjoy the advantages of the Active Distance Assist Distronic, the Active Speed Limit Assist and Urban Guard Plus providing an all-round monitoring of the parked car.

In addition, the new S-Class will be the first production car to optionally equip airbags designed to protect rear-seat passengers on both sides in a frontal impact. #MercedesBenz #SClass #CaresForWhatMatters

node.title: Safety, assistance and security in the new S-Class
